lockwise whirlpool sign at color Doppler US: an objective and definite sign of midgut volvulus. <em>Radiology</em> 1996;199(1):261–264.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiology.199.1.8633156">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8633156/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Clockwise+whirlpool+sign+at+color+Doppler+US%3A+an+objective+and+definite+sign+of+midgut+volvulus&amp;author=Y+Shimanuki&amp;author=T+Aihara&amp;author=H+Takano&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=261-264&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiology.199.1.8633156&amp;pmid=8633156">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="b9-0291281" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Fisher JK. Computed tomographic diagnosis of volvulus in intestinal malrotation. <em>Radiology</em> 1981; 140(1):145–146.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiology.140.1.7244217">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7244217/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Computed+tomographic+diagnosis+of+volvulus+in+intestinal+malrotation&amp;author=JK+Fisher&amp;publication_year=1981&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=145-146&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiology.140.1.7244217&amp;pmid=7244217">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="b10-0291281" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Ott DJ, Chen MY. Specific acute colonic disorders. <em>Radiol Clin North Am</em> 1994;32(5):871–884.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-